<h2>Calagator</h2>

<p style="color: gray; font-size: 80%; margin-top: -2em">
Calendar Aggregation With Teeth</p>

<p>Calagator is an all-volunteer effort to provide a unified calendar for technical communities and user groups in Portland, Oregon. Anyone can contribute information by importing, creating and editing entries.</p>

<p>You can also read our project news <%= link_to 'blog', blog_path %>, participate in <%= link_to 'discussions', forum_path %>, and report <%= link_to 'issues', issues_path %>. This site's <%= link_to 'software', code_path %> is all open-source and we're always looking for new people to join us in making the best calendar aggregator possible.</p>

<div id='coming_events'>
	<h2>What's happening?</h2>
	<h3>Today</h3>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @events_today, :opts => {:dates => false} } %>
	<h3>Tomorrow</h3>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @events_tomorrow, :opts => {:dates => false} } %>
	<h3>Later</h3>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @events_later } %>
</div>
<div id='recently_added_events'>
	<h2>Other Recent Additions</h2>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @recently_added_events } %>
</div>
